<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IoT & Drone-Based Flood Management</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <script defer src="script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>IoT & Drone-Based Disaster Management System</h1>
        <p>Enhancing Preparedness, Response & Recovery Using AI & Technology</p>
    </header>

    <section id="problem">
        <h2>🚨 Problem Statement</h2>
        <p>Frequent floods in Bihar & UP affect millions. Challenges include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>🚧 Delayed response & rescue operations</li>
            <li>⚠️ Lack of early warning systems</li>
            <li>📡 Communication breakdown during disasters</li>
            <li>📦 Resource distribution inefficiency</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="solution">
        <h2>💡 Our Solution</h2>
        <p>We combine IoT, AI, and Drones for better disaster management:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>🌊 IoT Sensors detect water levels & predict floods</li>
            <li>🧠 AI Dashboard helps authorities manage responses</li>
            <li>🚁 Drones assist in rescue & supply delivery</li>
            <li>📶 Emergency communication via network drones</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="dashboard.html" class="btn">View Live Dashboard</a>
    </section>

    <section id="survey">
        <h2>📝 Survey & Feedback</h2>
        <p>Your feedback helps us improve our disaster management system.</p>
        <form id="survey-form">
            <label for="name">Full Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

            <label for="rating">How effective is our system? (1-5):</label>
            <select id="rating" name="rating">
                <option value="5">5 - Excellent</option>
                <option value="4">4 - Good</option>
                <option value="3">3 - Average</option>
                <option value="2">2 - Needs Improvement</option>
                <option value="1">1 - Poor</option>
            </select>

            <label for="suggestions">Suggestions for Improvement:</label>
            <textarea id="suggestions" name="suggestions" rows="3"></textarea>

            <label>Would you recommend this system?</label>
            <input type="radio" id="yes" name="recommend" value="Yes" required>
            <label for="yes">Yes</label>
            <input type="radio" id="no" name="recommend" value="No">
            <label for="no">No</label>

            <button type="submit">Submit Feedback</button>
        </form>
        <p id="thank-you-message" style="display:none; color: lightgreen;">✅ Thank you for your feedback!</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>Created by Hacker Dude's | Contact: princeraj21dec2006@gmail.com</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
